social_posts.post_text:
I bought a 23’ Manual Toyota Supra! 
I thank God everyday for blessing with everything he’s given me. Since my s2k has been down I’ve wanted a fun daily. I have always loved the mk5’s but didn’t want the auto. As soon as the stick shift came out me, my brother, and my dad were looking for one. I want to thank my dad for going out of his way helping me find this car and dealing with different dealers. He also went to Orlando to get it without me knowing. I’m still in disbelief but I know when working hard and trying to do good, things like this happen. ❤️🙏
